 las claves necesarias para comprender la obra.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Theater / History & Criticism.2bisacsh1 aCasais Vila, Verónica, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2021z9783110753790oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertVervuert Complete eBook-Package 2020z9783110689631oZDB-207-IBV40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869035340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968690353423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783968690353.jpg  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-207-IBVb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DPKb2021